<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="no-js" lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About Us || KickCraze</title>
    <style>
        /* Global Styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh; /* Make sure the body takes the full height */
            overflow: hidden; /* Prevent overflow for glassmorphism */
        }

        /* Navigation Bar */
        .top-bar {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }

        .top-bar .title-area h1 a {
            color: #e46e24;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding-left: 20px;
            font-size: 1.8em;
        }

        .top-bar .right {
            list-style: none; /* This removes the bullet points */
            margin: 0;
            padding-right: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .top-bar li {
            padding: 0 10px;
        }

        .top-bar a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }

        .top-bar a:hover {
            color: #ddd;
        }

        /* Active link style */
        .top-bar .right .active a {
            text-decoration: underline; /* Adds an underline */
            color: #ddd; /* Change the color for active link */
        }

        /* Content Styles */
        .row {
            flex: 1; /* Allow the row to grow and take available space */
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center; /* Center content horizontally */
            align-items: center; /* Center content vertically */
        }

        /* Glassmorphism Box */
        .glassmorphism-box {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); /* Semi-transparent background */
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px); /* Increased blur effect */
            border-radius: 15px; /* Rounded corners */
            padding: 30px; /* Spacing inside the box */
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); /* Shadow for depth */
            max-width: 800px; /* Maximum width */
            text-align: center; /* Center text */
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); /* Optional border for contrast */
        }

        .row p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #000; /* Text color */
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #333; /* Match footer background color */
            color: #fff; /* Match footer text color */
            padding: 20px; /* Match footer padding */
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9em; /* Match footer font size */
        }

        footer p {
            color: #fff; /* Ensure footer text is white */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="top-bar">
        <div class="title-area">
          <h1><a href="/">KickCraze</a></h1>
        </div>
    
        <section class="top-bar-section">
            <!-- Right Nav Section -->
            <ul class="right">
                <li class="active"><a href="/about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="/products">Shoe Collection</a></li>
                <li><a href="/cart">View Cart</a></li>
                <li><a href="/orders">My Orders</a></li>
                <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
                <% if (user) { %> <!-- Check if user is logged in -->
                    <li><a href="/profile">My Account</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/logout">Log Out</a></li>
                <% } else { %> <!-- If not logged in, show login/register links -->
                    <li><a href="/login">Log In</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/register">Register</a></li>
                <% } %>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </nav>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="glassmorphism-box">
            <p>Welcome to KickCraze, your ultimate destination for premium footwear. Our mission is to provide a curated selection of high-quality shoes that cater to diverse tastes and preferences.</p>

            <p>At KickCraze, we believe that shoes are more than just an accessoryâ€”they're a statement of style and comfort. We strive to offer a unique range of products, including popular brands and exclusive lines that you won't find anywhere else.</p>

            <p>Why choose KickCraze? Our commitment to quality, exceptional customer service, and a seamless shopping experience sets us apart. Whether you're looking for a new pair of sneakers or a classic style, we're here to help you find the perfect footwear.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 KickCraze. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
